        <inline name="agenda item name">Israeli practices and settlement activities affecting the rights of the Palestinian People and other Arabs of the occupied territories</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 9 December 2021</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#fourthCommittee">[on the report of the Special Political and Decolonization Committee (Fourth Committee) (<inline name="originating document">A/76/417, para. 13</inline>)]</docProponent>
